---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Now - Juan Esquivel">
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
    <a href="/writing" class="nav-link">Writing</a>
    <a href="/stack" class="nav-link">Stack</a>
    <a href="/now" class="nav-link active">Now</a>
    <a href="/about" class="nav-link">About</a>
  </nav>

  <header class="page-header">
    <h1>Now</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">What I'm focused on at the moment.</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <h2>Work</h2>
    <p>I run marketing at StableLab, a crypto company helping on-chain businesses with growth intelligence. I spend a lot of time thinking about how to tell stories that actually land in crypto.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Building</h2>
    <p>Building a personal brand. Trying to connect with people who think about this stuff the same way I do and inspiring people in crypto to care about storytelling.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Life</h2>
    <p>Recently moved to Lisbon—still exploring neighborhoods, finding coffee spots, slowly learning Portuguese. Lifting weights consistently. Trying to read and cook more.</p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Listening</h2>
    <a href="https://open.spotify.com/user/caveatt" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="listening-link">Deftones, Junior H, Peso Pluma ↗</a>
  </section>

  <section class="watching-section">
    <h2>Watching</h2>

    <h3>Movies</h3>
    <a href="https://letterboxd.com/cadena/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="letterboxd-link">One Battle After Another, Bugonia, Weapons ↗</a>

    <h3>Shows</h3>
    <p class="watching-text">Entourage, Pluribus, IT: Welcome to Derry</p>

    <h3>Creators</h3>
    <p class="watching-text">George Heaton, Kai Cenat, Agent00, Daniel Simmons, Sam Sulek</p>
  </section>

  <p class="last-updated">Last updated: January 2026</p>
</Layout>

<style>
  .nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
  }

  .nav-link {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: #525252;
    transition: color 0.15s ease;
  }

  .nav-link:hover {
    color: #c4c4c4;
  }

  .nav-link.active {
    color: #e5e5e5;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #e5e5e5;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    color: #999999;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section h2 {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #525252;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  section p {
    color: #c4c4c4;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .last-updated {
    color: #404040;
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-style: italic;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  /* Watching */
  .watching-section h3 {
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #999999;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
  }

  .watching-section h3:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .watching-text {
    color: #c4c4c4;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .letterboxd-link {
    color: #c4c4c4;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .letterboxd-link:hover {
    color: #00E054;
  }

  /* Listening */
  .listening-link {
    color: #c4c4c4;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .listening-link:hover {
    color: #1DB954;
  }
</style>
